<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="da" class="dark">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>LearnAI DK | Lær AI på dansk</title>
    <meta name="description" content="LearnAI DK — Lær AI på dansk fra nybegynder til ekspert.">
    
    <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/three.js/r128/three.min.js"></script>

    <style>
        /* ==========================================
           1. DESIGN SYSTEM & VARIABLES
           ========================================== */
        :root {
            --bg-dark: #000000;
            --bg-gradient: #0a0a1f;
            --accent-cyan: #00eaff;
            --accent-cyan-dim: rgba(0, 234, 255, 0.15);
            
            --lvl-d: #10b981; /* Grøn */
            --lvl-c: #3b82f6; /* Blå */
            --lvl-b: #8b5cf6; /* Lilla */
            --lvl-a: #fbbf24; /* Guld */

            --text-main: #ffffff;
            --text-muted: #888899;
            --border-glass: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
            --bg-glass: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.02);

            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Inter", "Segoe UI", Roboto, sans-serif;
        }

        @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
            * {
                animation-duration: 0.01ms !important;
                animation-iteration-count: 1 !important;
                transition-duration: 0.01ms !important;
                scroll-behavior: auto !important;
            }
        }

        * {
            box-sizing: border-box;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        html {
            scroll-behavior: smooth;
        }

        body {
            background-color: var(--bg-dark);
            background-image: radial-gradient(circle at top center, #0d0d2b 0%, var(--bg-dark) 100%);
            color: var(--text-main);
            overflow-x: hidden;
            line-height: 1.6;
            -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
        }

        /* ==========================================
           2. TYPOGRAPHY & UTILITIES
           ========================================== */
        h1, h2, h3, h4 {
            font-weight: 700;
            line-height: 1.2;
            letter-spacing: -0.03em;
        }

        h2 { font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3rem); margin-bottom: 1rem; }
        h3 { font-size: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
        p { color: var(--text-muted); margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }

        .text-gradient {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ffffff 0%, var(--accent-cyan) 100%);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
            background-clip: text;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 0 2rem;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 10;
        }

        .btn {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            padding: 0.8rem 1.5rem;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-weight: 600;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: all 0.2s ease;
            cursor: pointer;
            border: 1px solid transparent;
        }

        .btn-primary {
            background: var(--text-main);
            color: var(--bg-dark);
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px var(--accent-cyan-dim);
        }

        .btn-primary:hover {
            background: var(--accent-cyan);
            box-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(0, 234, 255, 0.4);
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }

        .btn-outline {
            background: transparent;
            color: var(--text-main);
            border-color: var(--border-glass);
        }

        .btn-outline:hover {
            background: var(--bg-glass);
            border-color: var(--accent-cyan);
        }

        .glass-panel {
            background: var(--bg-glass);
            backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
            -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
            border: 1px solid var(--border-glass);
            border-radius: 16px;
        }

        .reveal {
            opacity: 0;
            transform: translateY(30px);
            transition: opacity 0.8s ease, transform 0.8s ease;
        }

        .reveal.visible {
            opacity: 1;
            transform: translateY(0);
        }

        /* ==========================================
           3. THREE.JS CANVAS
           ========================================== */
        #webgl-canvas {
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100vw;
            height: 100vh;
            z-index: 0;
            pointer-events: none; /* Lader musen interagere med DOM under */
        }

        /* ==========================================
           4. SECTIONS
           ========================================== */
        
        /* Navigation */
        nav {
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            width: 100%;
            padding: 1.5rem 0;
            z-index: 100;
            border-bottom: 1px solid transparent;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }
        nav.scrolled {
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7);
            backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-glass);
            padding: 1rem 0;
        }
        .nav-inner {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
        }
        .logo {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: var(--text-main);
            text-decoration: none;
            letter-spacing: -0.05em;
        }

        /* Hero */
        .hero {
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            padding-top: 5rem;
        }
        .hero h1 {
            font-size: clamp(3rem, 8vw, 6rem);
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        }
        .hero-content {
            max-width: 800px;
        }
        .hero-buttons {
            display: flex;
            gap: 1rem;
            margin-top: 2rem;
        }

        /* Stats */
        .stats-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
            gap: 1.5rem;
            margin: -4rem auto 4rem;
        }
        .stat-card {
            padding: 2rem;
            text-align: center;
            transition: border-color 0.3s ease;
        }
        .stat-card:hover {
            border-color: var(--accent-cyan);
        }
        .stat-val {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: var(--text-main);
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }

        /* Hovedkurser (Med 3D integration via DOM placering) */
        section {
            padding: 6rem 0;
        }
        .section-header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 4rem;
        }
        .course-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
            gap: 2rem;
        }
        .course-card {
            position: relative;
            padding: 2rem;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            transition: transform 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.175, 0.885, 0.32, 1.275), box-shadow 0.4s ease;
            overflow: hidden;
            cursor: default;
        }
        /* 3D placeholder div - definerer hvor 3D krystallen skal tegnes */
        .crystal-placeholder {
            width: 100%;
            height: 180px;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }
        
        .course-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-10px);
        }
        .course-card[data-level="D"]:hover { box-shadow: 0 10px 40px rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.15); border-color: var(--lvl-d); }
        .course-card[data-level="C"]:hover { box-shadow: 0 10px 40px rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.15); border-color: var(--lvl-c); }
        .course-card[data-level="B"]:hover { box-shadow: 0 10px 40px rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.15); border-color: var(--lvl-b); }
        .course-card[data-level="A"]:hover { box-shadow: 0 10px 40px rgba(251, 191, 36, 0.15); border-color: var(--lvl-a); }

        .course-badge {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 0.25rem 0.75rem;
            border-radius: 99px;
            font-size: 0.75rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.05em;
        }
        .course-card[data-level="D"] .course-badge { background: rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.1); color: var(--lvl-d); }
        .course-card[data-level="C"] .course-badge { background: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.1); color: var(--lvl-c); }
        .course-card[data-level="B"] .course-badge { background: rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.1); color: var(--lvl-b); }
        .course-card[data-level="A"] .course-badge { background: rgba(251, 191, 36, 0.1); color: var(--lvl-a); }

        .price {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin: 1rem 0;
        }
        .req {
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            color: var(--text-muted);
            margin-top: auto;
            padding-top: 1rem;
            border-top: 1px solid var(--border-glass);
        }

        /* Sidekurser */
        .side-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(240px, 1fr));
            gap: 1.5rem;
        }
        .side-card {
            padding: 1.5rem;
            transition: border-color 0.3s;
        }
        .side-card:hover {
            border-color: var(--accent-cyan);
        }
        .side-card h3 { font-size: 1.2rem; }

        /* Kursus Indhold Preview (Tabs) */
        .tabs-container {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 2rem;
            margin-top: 3rem;
        }
        @media(min-width: 768px) {
            .tabs-container { flex-direction: row; }
        }
        .tab-buttons {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 0.5rem;
            min-width: 200px;
        }
        .tab-btn {
            background: transparent;
            border: 1px solid var(--border-glass);
            color: var(--text-muted);
            padding: 1rem;
            text-align: left;
            border-radius: 8px;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-size: 1rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            transition: all 0.2s;
        }
        .tab-btn:hover { background: var(--bg-glass); color: var(--text-main); }
        .tab-btn.active {
            background: var(--bg-glass);
            border-color: var(--accent-cyan);
            color: var(--accent-cyan);
        }
        .tab-content {
            flex-grow: 1;
            display: none;
            padding: 2rem;
            animation: fadeIn 0.4s ease;
        }
        .tab-content.active { display: block; }
        .module-list { list-style: none; }
        .module-list li {
            padding: 1rem 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-glass);
            display: flex;
            align-items: flex-start;
            gap: 1rem;
        }
        .module-list li:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
        .module-icon { color: var(--accent-cyan); font-weight: bold; }

        /* Sådan virker det */
        .steps-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(220px, 1fr));
            gap: 2rem;
            position: relative;
        }
        .step {
            text-align: left;
            position: relative;
            padding: 2rem;
        }
        .step-num {
            font-size: 3rem;
            font-weight: 800;
            color: var(--border-glass);
            position: absolute;
            top: 0.5rem;
            right: 1.5rem;
            z-index: -1;
            transition: color 0.3s;
        }
        .step:hover .step-num { color: var(--accent-cyan-dim); }

        /* Eksamen Info */
        .exam-info {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 2rem;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: space-between;
        }
        .exam-details { flex: 1; min-width: 300px; }
        .exam-scores {
            flex: 1;
            min-width: 300px;
            background: rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
            padding: 2rem;
            border-radius: 12px;
            border: 1px solid var(--border-glass);
        }
        .score-row {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            padding: 0.5rem 0;
            border-bottom: 1px dashed var(--border-glass);
        }
        .score-row:last-child { border: none; }

        /* FAQ Accordion */
        details {
            background: var(--bg-glass);
            border: 1px solid var(--border-glass);
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        summary {
            padding: 1.5rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            cursor: pointer;
            list-style: none;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            outline: none;
        }
        summary::-webkit-details-marker { display: none; }
        summary::after {
            content: '+';
            color: var(--accent-cyan);
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            transition: transform 0.3s;
        }
        details[open] summary::after { transform: rotate(45deg); }
        .faq-content {
            padding: 0 1.5rem 1.5rem;
            color: var(--text-muted);
        }

        /* Footer */
        footer {
            border-top: 1px solid var(--border-glass);
            padding: 4rem 0 2rem;
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 4rem;
        }

        @keyframes fadeIn {
            from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(10px); }
            to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .hero-buttons { flex-direction: column; }
            .hero h1 { line-height: 1.1; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <canvas id="webgl-canvas" aria-hidden="true"></canvas>

    <nav id="navbar">
        <div class="container nav-inner">
            <a href="#" class="logo">LearnAI DK</a>
            <div>
                <a href="#kurser" class="btn btn-primary" style="padding: 0.5rem 1rem; font-size: 0.9rem;">Start gratis</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <section class="hero container">
        <div class="hero-content reveal">
            <h1>Lær AI på dansk <br><span class="text-gradient">fra nybegynder til ekspert</span></h1>
            <p style="font-size: 1.25rem; max-width: 600px;">
                En premium uddannelsesplatform designet til at give dig praktiske AI-færdigheder. Tag kontrol over fremtidens værktøjer i dit eget tempo.
            </p>
            <div class="hero-buttons">
                <a href="#kurser" class="btn btn-primary">Start gratis med Kursus D</a>
                <a href="#indhold" class="btn btn-outline">Se pensum</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <div class="container stats-grid reveal">
        <div class="glass-panel stat-card">
            <div class="stat-val">4</div>
            <p class="m-0">Klargjorte niveauer</p>
        </div>
        <div class="glass-panel stat-card">
            <div class="stat-val text-gradient">100%</div>
            <p class="m-0">På dansk</p>
        </div>
        <div class="glass-panel stat-card">
            <div class="stat-val" style="color: var(--lvl-d)">Gratis</div>
            <p class="m-0">At starte rejsen</p>
        </div>
        <div class="glass-panel stat-card">
            <div class="stat-val">Bevis</div>
            <p class="m-0">Efter endt eksamen</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <section id="kurser" class="container">
        <div class="section-header reveal">
            <h2 class="text-gradient">Hovedkurser</h2>
            <p>Din strukturerede vej mod AI-mesterskab. Vælg dit startpunkt.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="course-grid">
            <div class="glass-panel course-card reveal" data-level="D">
                <div class="crystal-placeholder"></div>
                <span class="course-badge">Niveau D</span>
                <h3>Nybegynder</h3>
                <p>Fra nul til at bruge AI i hverdagen og forstå de grundlæggende koncepter.</p>
                <div class="price" style="color: var(--lvl-d)">Gratis</div>
                <a href="#" class="btn btn-outline" style="width: 100%;">Tilmeld</a>
                <div class="req">Ingen konto krævet</div>
            </div>

            <div class="glass-panel course-card reveal" data-level="C" style="transition-delay: 0.1s;">
                <div class="crystal-placeholder"></div>
                <span class="course-badge">Niveau C</span>
                <h3>Mellemniveau</h3>
                <p>Gå fra average til en stærk og bevidst bruger af AI i dit arbejde.</p>
                <div class="price">99 kr</div>
                <a href="#" class="btn btn-outline" style="width: 100%;">Lås op</a>
                <div class="req">Krav: Bestået Kursus D</div>
            </div>

            <div class="glass-panel course-card reveal" data-level="B" style="transition-delay: 0.2s;">
                <div class="crystal-placeholder"></div>
                <span class="course-badge">Niveau B</span>
                <h3>Øvet</h3>
                <p>Lær avancerede workflows, RAG, og agenter. Bliv den lokale AI-specialist.</p>
                <div class="price">199 kr</div>
                <a href="#" class="btn btn-outline" style="width: 100%;">Lås op</a>
                <div class="req">Krav: Bestået Kursus C</div>
            </div>

            <div class="glass-panel course-card reveal" data-level="A" style="transition-delay: 0.3s;">
                <div class="crystal-placeholder"></div>
                <span class="course-badge">Niveau A</span>
                <h3>Ekspert</h3>
                <p>Forstå modellerne i dybden, sikkerhed, og enterprise-implementering.</p>
                <div class="price">299 kr</div>
                <a href="#" class="btn btn-outline" style="width: 100%;">Lås op</a>
                <div class="req">Krav: Bestået Kursus B</div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="container">
        <div class="section-header reveal">
            <h2>Specialiseringer</h2>
            <p>Dyk ned i specifikke niche-værktøjer med vores sidekurser.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="side-grid">
            <div class="glass-panel side-card reveal">
                <h3>AI-værktøjer niv. 1</h3>
                <p style="font-size: 0.9rem;">De vigtigste apps udover ChatGPT.</p>
                <div style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; margin-top: 1rem;">
                    <span style="font-weight: 700;">79 kr</span>
                    <span style="font-size: 0.8rem; color: var(--text-muted);">Anbefalet: Kursus C</span>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="glass-panel side-card reveal">
                <h3>AI-værktøjer niv. 2</h3>
                <p style="font-size: 0.9rem;">Avancerede værktøjer for nørder.</p>
                <div style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; margin-top: 1rem;">
                    <span style="font-weight: 700;">99 kr</span>
                    <span style="font-size: 0.8rem; color: var(--text-muted);">Anbefalet: Kursus C</span>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="glass-panel side-card reveal">
                <h3>Tjene penge på AI</h3>
                <p style="font-size: 0.9rem;">Monetisering og forretningsmodeller.</p>
                <div style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; margin-top: 1rem;">
                    <span style="font-weight: 700;">149 kr</span>
                    <span style="font-size: 0.8rem; color: var(--text-muted);">Anbefalet: Kursus B</span>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="glass-panel side-card reveal">
                <h3>Lær andre AI</h3>
                <p style="font-size: 0.9rem;">Pædagogik og AI i organisationer.</p>
                <div style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; margin-top: 1rem;">
                    <span style="font-weight: 700;">99 kr</span>
                    <span style="font-size: 0.8rem; color: var(--text-muted);">Anbefalet: Kursus C</span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="indhold" class="container">
        <div class="section-header reveal">
            <h2>Kursusindhold</h2>
            <p>Interaktivt pensum. Klik på niveauerne for at se detaljer.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="tabs-container reveal">
            <div class="tab-buttons">
                <button class="tab-btn active" data-target="tab-d">Kursus D (Gratis)</button>
                <button class="tab-btn" data-target="tab-c">Kursus C</button>
                <button class="tab-btn" data-target="tab-b">Kursus B</button>
                <button class="tab-btn" data-target="tab-a">Kursus A</button>
            </div>
            
            <div class="glass-panel tab-content active" id="tab-d">
                <h3 style="color: var(--lvl-d)">Niveau D: Nybegynder</h3>
                <p>4 moduler · Ca. 1 time læsning</p>
                <ul class="module-list">
                    <li><span class="module-icon">01</span><div><strong>Hvad er AI?</strong><br><span style="font-size:0.9rem; color:var(--text-muted)">En simpel, ikke-teknisk introduktion.</span></div></li>
                    <li><span class="module-icon">02</span><div><strong>Din første AI-samtale</strong><br><span style="font-size:0.9rem; color:var(--text-muted)">Sådan opretter du en konto og starter.</span></div></li>
                    <li><span class="module-icon">03</span><div><strong>Gode prompts</strong><br><span style="font-size:0.9rem; color:var(--text-muted)">De 3 gyldne regler: Vær specifik, giv kontekst, bed om format.</span></div></li>
                    <li><span class="module-icon">04</span><div><strong>Sikkerhed & Faldgruber</strong><br><span style="font-size:0.9rem; color:var(--text-muted)">Hallucinationer, privatliv og dobbelttjek af fakta.</span></div></li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="glass-panel tab-content" id="tab-c">
                <h3 style="color: var(--lvl-c)">Niveau C: Mellemniveau</h3>
                <p>3 dele · 45 min - 1,5 time</p>
                <ul class="module-list">
                    <li><span class="module-icon">C1</span><div><strong>Prompt-teknik</strong><br><span style="font-size:0.9rem; color:var(--text-muted)">Rolleprompt, kædetænkning, iterativ forfining og negativ afgrænsning.</span></div></li>
                    <li><span class="module-icon">C2</span><div><strong>Emails og produktivitet</strong><br><span style="font-size:0.9rem; color:var(--text-muted)">Automatisering af tekstarbejde i hverdagen.</span></div></li>
                    <li><span class="module-icon">C3</span><div><strong>AI til rapporter og møder</strong><br><span style="font-size:0.9rem; color:var(--text-muted)">Syntese af store mængder data på sekunder.</span></div></li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="glass-panel tab-content" id="tab-b">
                <h3 style="color: var(--lvl-b)">Niveau B: Øvet</h3>
                <p>5 dele · Avanceret brug</p>
                <ul class="module-list">
                    <li><span class="module-icon">B1</span><div><strong>Avanceret prompting</strong><br><span style="font-size:0.9rem; color:var(--text-muted)">System prompts og struktureret output.</span></div></li>
